TodoX ROADMAP

- API endpoints
  - Users
    - /api/auth/register                          -> POST
    - /api/auth/login                             -> POST
    - /api/auth/verify                            -> POST
    - /api/auth                                   -> GET

  - Todo lists
    - /api/todolists                              -> GET
    - /api/todolists/{id}                         -> GET
    - /api/todolists                              -> POST
    - /api/todolists/{id}                         -> PUT
    - /api/todolists/{id}                         -> DELETE

  - Todo items
    - /api/todolists/{listId}/items               -> GET
    - /api/todolists/{listId}/items/{id}          -> GET
    - /api/todolists/{listId}/items               -> POST
    - /api/todolists/{listId}/items/{id}          -> PUT
    - /api/todolists/{listId}/items/{id}/complete -> PATCH
    - /api/todolists/{listId}/items/{id}          -> DELETE

- Entity Relationships
  - User     1 : 0-N TodoList
  - TodoList 1 : 0-N TodoItem